    cbalance utxo + fees + dep + donations + wdls * 0 ≡⟨ cong (cbalance utxo + fees + dep + donations +_ ) (*-zeroʳ wdls) ⟩
    cbalance utxo + fees + dep + donations + 0 ≡⟨ +-identityʳ _ ⟩
    cbalance utxo + fees + dep + donations ≡⟨ cong (λ x → x + dep + donations) $ begin
